    "section_image_with_text_WecFR8": {
      "type": "section-image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "image_mAXfG7": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Pro-Formance-54-e1559579796967.jpg",
            "video": "",
            "video_button_color": "primary",
            "title": "",
            "desc": "<h3>Residential Hoop Installation</h3><p>Whether you opt for an in-ground or wall-mount basketball hoop in Chicago, we’ll visit your property and ensure the highest quality installation. If you need advice regarding placement or hoop type, our family is always happy to help.</p><h3>Commercial Hoop Installation </h3><p>We have extensive experience in installing both in-ground and wall-mount hoops in schools, gyms, and other commercial settings. When you buy basketball hoops, you have extra rules and regulations around safety, so you need to partner with a professional service you can trust. <br/></p>",
            "horizontal_align": "left",
            "link_title": "Contact Us",
            "link": "https://theguyon41.com/pages/free-estimate",
            "bg_color_block": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "bg_color_content": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "color_text": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "text_heading_color": true,
            "text_border_color": true
          }
        },
        "image_CtzEhV": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Hoop-works-lowered.jpg",
            "video": "",
            "video_button_color": "primary",
            "title": "",
            "desc": "<h3>Basketball Hoop Maintenance/Repair</h3><p>The best way to extend the life of your basketball hoop set is to look after it, and this means performing regular maintenance and repairs. Rather than adding to your own to-do list, allow our friendly team to check, tighten, and lubricate in all the right places. </p><h3>Hoop Removal </h3><p>If you’ve had your in-ground hoop for many years, and you’re ready for an upgrade, we can also help you remove the old hoop. It has created many memories and been a reliable partner, but it’s now time to utilize the amazing modern hoops available at Fenceworks.</p><h3>Hoop Relocation </h3><p>We can safely and efficiently move your basketball hoop from its current location to a new space. Whether residential or <a href=\"https://theguyon41.com/collections/commercial-play-sets\">commercial</a>, you don’t need to regret your basketball hoop purchase. Instead, get more value from it in a new location. <br/></p>",
            "horizontal_align": "left",
            "link_title": "Fenceworks Basketball FAQ'S",
            "link": "https://theguyon41.com/pages/basketball-faqs-your-questions-answered-by-fenceworks",
            "bg_color_block": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "bg_color_content": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "color_text": "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            "text_heading_color": true,
            "text_border_color": true
          }
        }
