    "section_rich_text_KBibYF": {
      "type": "section-rich-text",
      "name": "Rich text",
      "settings": {
        "section_title": "Why Choose Fenceworks?",
        "text": "<p>When you choose <a href=\"https://theguyon41.com/\">Fenceworks</a>, you’re not going for a big box retailer that doesn’t know your name. You’re not going for an online retailer that isn’t passionate about the quality of the product. You’re choosing a member of the community, a family in Chicago, just like yours. </p><p>We first opened in 1967, and we’re proud to have helped thousands of people since, whether with fencing, playsets, trampolines, or basketball hoops in Chicago. Every transition our business goes through is to better serve our customers, and we now have three generations of our family within the business. </p><p>We’ll visit your home to provide advice, and we only ever put our name to the highest-quality products, including basketball hoops. To learn more about our products or our mission, <a href=\"https://theguyon41.com/pages/free-estimate\" title=\"https://theguyon41.com/pages/free-estimate\">get in touch today</a>. You’re also welcome to visit our Northbrook showroom - we’d love to see you! </p>",
        "section_width": "tiny",
        "padding_top": 0,
        "padding_bottom": 0,
        "section_bottom_margin": false
      }
    },
